# Savia Web — Infrastructure (.acm)
> hash: sha256:auto | generated: 2026-03-30 | lines: 62

## Composables (Data Access Layer — 3 total)

### useBridge
- **File**: `src/composables/useBridge.ts`
- **Purpose**: REST API client to Savia Bridge backend
- **Methods**: get<T>(path), post<T>(path, body), healthCheck(), baseUrl(), headers()
- **Auth**: Bearer token from useAuthStore
- **Error handling**: catch blocks return null
- **Base URL**: https://localhost:8922 (configurable via auth store)

### useSSE
- **File**: `src/composables/useSSE.ts`
- **Purpose**: Server-Sent Events streaming for chat (cancelable)
- **Methods**: streamChat(message, sessionId, onEvent), sendPermission(requestId, granted), cancelStream()
- **Events**: StreamEvent (text|start|done|error|tool_use|permission_request)
- **Pattern**: POST to /chat with interactive=true, parse SSE events

### useReportData<T>
- **File**: `src/composables/useReportData.ts`
- **Purpose**: Generic report data fetcher with project scoping
- **Methods**: load(extraParams)
- **Returns**: data, loading, error (reactive refs)
- **Auto-reload**: watches projectStore.selectedId

## Bridge Endpoints Used

| Endpoint | Method | Composable | Used By |
|----------|--------|------------|---------|
| `/auth/me` | GET | useBridge | Router guard |
| `/chat` | POST (SSE) | useSSE | ChatPage |
| `/sessions` | GET | useBridge | ChatStore |
| `/projects` | GET | useBridge | ProjectStore |
| `/backlog?project={id}` | GET | useBridge | BacklogStore |
| `/files` | GET | useBridge | FileBrowserPage |
| `/files/content` | GET | useBridge | FileViewer |
| `/dashboard?project={id}` | GET | useBridge | DashboardStore |
| `/users` | GET | useBridge | AdminUsersPage |
| `/users/{slug}` | GET/PUT | useBridge | ProfilePage |
| `/users/{slug}/rotate-token` | POST | useBridge | AdminUsersPage |
| `/reports/*` | GET | useReportData | Report pages |

## Persistence Layer

| Store | Mechanism | Key |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Auth | localStorage | savia-web-auth |
| Chat | localStorage (watch) | savia-web-chat-sessions |
| Backlog | localStorage (watch) | savia-web-backlog-filters |
| Project | localStorage | savia-web-project |

## External Dependencies

- Savia Bridge (HTTPS, port 8922, TLS self-signed in dev)
- No direct database access (all via Bridge REST API)
- No external CDN dependencies (bundled with Vite)
